{"id":232958476,"title":"#分享 ios版本 Line語言調整","content":"我不確定分享這個板是否正確，如有錯誤，歡迎指正\n是這樣的，以前偶然發現Line可以調成英文版本\n以至於後來就用習慣了，一直沒有更改回來。\n直到最近朋友和我說：「欸欸，妳的line有沒有強制被切回中文版本？而且Line的設定也沒有語言了」\n我才去了解了一下。\n提供給IOS系統的人\n❗️ios13、6以上機種❗️\n打開系統設定—並搜尋Line的App\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/c62dd688-2b94-4e19-bfa3-61a1b53a0cea/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/44618754-c274-4b01-8b01-6e25ccc36f4e/1280.jpeg\n就可以在裡面更換語言啦❗️\n\n好的👌這只是冷門的分享，並不是所有人都需要。","excerpt":"我不確定分享這個板是否正確，如有錯誤，歡迎指正，是這樣的，以前偶然發現Line可以調成英文版本，以至於後來就用習慣了，一直沒有更改回來。直到最近朋友和我說：「欸欸，妳的line有沒有強制被切回中文版本","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"577f29b9-ef96-4e05-9e79-55e2a7d6e3db","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-25T21:00:31.484Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T21:01:26.656Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":5,"tags":[],"topics":["LINE","iOS"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"App","forumAlias":"app","school":"中國科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":5}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/c62dd688-2b94-4e19-bfa3-61a1b53a0cea/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/44618754-c274-4b01-8b01-6e25ccc36f4e/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"36156a88-9c7f-465a-9e8f-43a1dd8ceb1e","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/c62dd688-2b94-4e19-bfa3-61a1b53a0cea/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/c62dd688-2b94-4e19-bfa3-61a1b53a0cea/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/c62dd688-2b94-4e19-bfa3-61a1b53a0cea/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-25T21:00:31.484Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-25T21:01:26.656Z","width":482,"height":640},{"id":"36156a88-9c7f-